By Representative Hendricks of New Bedford and Senator Montigny, a joint petition
(accompanied by bill, House, No. 2864) of Christopher Hendricks and Antonio F. D. Cabral
(with the approval of the mayor and city council) that the city of New Bedford Retirement Board
be authorized to provide certain retirement benefits to Lavar Gilbert, a police detective of said
city. Public Service. [Local Approval Received.]
